00:13:54.150 --> 00:13:56.650
it's like 1024 pixels wide
when you supply it.

00:13:56.650 --> 00:13:58.720
And so people get tempted
to cram all kinds of

00:13:58.720 --> 00:13:59.910
information in there.

00:13:59.910 --> 00:14:02.060
But really, really
resist that.

00:14:02.060 --> 00:14:04.052
Because it can be shown
very, very small.

00:14:04.052 --> 00:14:07.120
If you think about a small
handset, kind of three inches

00:14:07.120 --> 00:14:10.460
diagonally handset, it's going
to be shrunken down greatly.

00:14:10.460 --> 00:14:13.140
So my advice to people
is always to get

00:14:13.140 --> 00:14:13.800
your feature graphic.

00:14:13.800 --> 00:14:15.980
And resize it down to about
100 pixels wide.

00:14:15.980 --> 00:14:18.660
And check that everything's
kind of legible and still

00:14:18.660 --> 00:14:20.540
looks good at that
kind of size.

00:14:20.540 --> 00:14:22.435
And the other tip is that if
you are lucky enough to get

00:14:22.435 --> 00:14:26.210
