00:14:40.250 --> 00:14:42.465
So really have it kind
of stand alone.

00:14:42.465 --> 00:14:42.920
ROMAN NURIK: Yeah.

00:14:42.920 --> 00:14:44.950
And it could appear without
the icon and

00:14:44.950 --> 00:14:45.880
appear without the title.

00:14:45.880 --> 00:14:47.580
So absolutely.

00:14:47.580 --> 00:14:49.790
That it can appear standalone
is a very, very important

00:14:49.790 --> 00:14:51.300
point for future graphics.

00:14:51.300 --> 00:14:53.110
NICK: And resist putting
