the multi select mode and

00:17:13.800 --> 00:17:15.410
contextual action bar.

00:17:15.410 --> 00:17:17.160
Those are really important
modes.

00:17:17.160 --> 00:17:20.210
And you should really make
sure that there's touch

00:17:20.210 --> 00:17:23.270
indicators when you're in
the multi select mode.

